#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.nlargest.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.nlargest"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:1 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows ordered by `columns` in descending order."
msgstr "返回按 `columns` 降序排列的前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:3 of
msgid ""
"Return the first `n` rows with the largest values in `columns`, in "
"descending order. The columns that are not specified are returned as "
"well, but not used for ordering."
msgstr ""
"返回 `columns` 中具有最大值的前 `n` 行，按降序排列。未指定的列也会返回，"
"但不用于排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:7 of
msgid ""
"This method is equivalent to ``df.sort_values(columns, "
"ascending=False).head(n)``, but more performant."
msgstr ""
"此方法等效于 ``df.sort_values(columns, ascending=False).head(n)``，但性能"
"更优。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:11 of
msgid "Number of rows to return."
msgstr "要返回的行数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:13 of
msgid "Column label(s) to order by."
msgstr "用于排序的列标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:15 of
msgid ""
"Where there are duplicate values:  - `first` : prioritize the first "
"occurrence(s) - `last` : prioritize the last occurrence(s) - ``all`` : do"
" not drop any duplicates, even it means             selecting more than "
"`n` items."
msgstr ""
"当存在重复值时：  - `first` ：优先选择首次出现的值 - `last` ：优先选择"
"最后出现的值 - ``all`` ：不删除任何重复项，即使这意味着选择超过 `n` 个项"
"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:15 of
msgid "Where there are duplicate values:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:17 of
msgid "`first` : prioritize the first occurrence(s)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:18 of
msgid "`last` : prioritize the last occurrence(s)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:19 of
msgid "``all``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:-1 of
msgid "do not drop any duplicates, even it means"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:20 of
msgid "selecting more than `n` items."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:23 of
msgid "The first `n` rows ordered by the given columns in descending order."
msgstr "按给定列降序排列的前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.nsmallest`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:30 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows ordered by `columns` in ascending order."
msgstr "返回按 `columns` 升序排列的前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.sort_values`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:33 of
msgid "Sort DataFrame by the values."
msgstr "按值对 DataFrame 进行排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.head`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:36 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows without re-ordering."
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行，不重新排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:40 of
msgid ""
"This function cannot be used with all column types. For example, when "
"specifying columns with `object` or `category` dtypes, ``TypeError`` is "
"raised."
msgstr ""
"此函数不能用于所有列类型。例如，当指定具有 `object` 或 `category` "
"数据类型的列时，会引发 ``TypeError``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:45 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:69 of
msgid ""
"In the following example, we will use ``nlargest`` to select the three "
"rows having the largest values in column \"population\"."
msgstr ""
"在以下示例中，我们将使用 ``nlargest`` 选择在 \"population\" 列中具有"
"最大值的三行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:78 of
msgid "When using ``keep='last'``, ties are resolved in reverse order:"
msgstr "当使用 ``keep='last'`` 时，重复项按相反顺序处理："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:86 of
msgid "When using ``keep='all'``, all duplicate items are maintained:"
msgstr "当使用 ``keep='all'`` 时，所有重复项都会保留："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.df_nlargest:96 of
msgid ""
"To order by the largest values in column \"population\" and then \"GDP\","
" we can specify multiple columns like in the next example."
msgstr ""
"要按列 \"population\" 和 \"GDP\" 中的最大值进行排序，我们可以在下一个示例"
"中指定多个列。"

